		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>[[/save charisma]]{Charisma Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes 8d6 force damage* and is &amp;reference[cursed]. While cursed in this way, if the target reaches 0 hit points while under the effects of this curse, the target instantly dies, and their body and soul becomes permanently cursed, preventing them from being raised from the dead.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>*<strong>Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 2d6 force]]{2d6} for each spell level above 7th.</p><p></p><p><em>Removing the curse on a creature slain by Curse of Doom will allow them to be raised again.</em></p>",
